<ref name=obsolete>xChat is no longer being developed by its original creators. Hexchat is entirely based on xChat and is now designed by new people.</ref>
<ref name=opera>Opera 12.xx was the last version with IRC support. When Opera was rebased from Opera's own Presto layout engine to the Chromium browser, IRC and Mail were not ported.</ref>

